					<p class="ja-typo-icon icon-doc"></p>
					<h3 style="text-align: justify;">Contact:</h3>
					<p style="text-align: justify;">Mukesh Patel School of Technology Management &amp; Engineering,<br> Behind Homeopathy College,<br> Bhakti VedantaSwami Marg, JVPD Scheme,<br> Vile-Parle (west), Mumbai - 400 056.<br> Tel: +91 022-26717970/71, +91 022-26201790/91<br> Website: <a href="http://engineering.nmims.edu/" target="_blank">http://engineering.nmims.edu/</a></p>
					<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
					<h3 style="text-align: justify;">Verdict:</h3>
					<p style="text-align: justify;">NMIMS's Mukesh Patel is a brilliant college to go to if you want to enjoy a royal life. It’s a rare combination of studies, crowd and life but the fees are exorbitantly high which is a huge minus for many middle class families. Meeting people from diversified background is one of the strongest points of this college.</p>	</section>



